<text>Vampyroteuthidae is a family of vampyromorph cephalopods containing the extant vampire squid, &quot;Vampyroteuthis infernalis&quot;, and the extinct genera &quot;Necroteuthis&quot;, &quot;Provampyroteuthis&quot; and &quot;Vampyronassa&quot;.

